            <a href="/partquiz/4" method="GET "><h3>Quiz</h3></a>
            <h3>Progress</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="right">
          <img src="images/part4.png " alt="" style="object-fit: cover" />
          <p>
            The Directive Principles are guidelines for the framing of laws by
            the government. These principles aim to create a social order
            characterized by social, economic, and political justice.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
